"44800d060b6b72b886b43d3ee27312321d2fca9d","tid":82773,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到美人魚真係屌<span style=\"color: red;\">出</span>聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n其實美人魚我收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7779ae8060f1c245143bc82304f4518ee854bcb","tid":82773,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到美人魚真係屌<span style=\"color: red;\">出</span>聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<strong>教化而不說教，亦為港人困境的寫照。人魚世界面臨外來同化瀕死威脅，只有游出去才能得自由，是合拍片大潮下難得視野完整及保持自我的情懷之作。</strong><br />\n周生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為評論學會係會捧下危城、三人行，點估到係美人魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd367cba11862b11a8848ff5ceeaebd1cafa9bc","tid":82773,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到美人魚真係屌<span style=\"color: red;\">出</span>聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<strong>教化而不說教，亦為港人困境的寫照。人魚世界面臨外來同化瀕死威脅，只有游出去才能得自由，是合拍片大潮下難得視野完整及保持自我的情懷之作。</strong><br />\n周生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為評論學會係會捧下危城、三人行，點估到係美人魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為佢地會捧擺渡人 (都有個推薦電影)，無人估到佢地會鍾意美人魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbf9286d357a0e8aacc9163ab1ec954208c32b9","tid":82773,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到美人魚真係屌<span style=\"color: red;\">出</span>聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<strong>教化而不說教，亦為港人困境的寫照。人魚世界面臨外來同化瀕死威脅，只有游出去才能得自由，是合拍片大潮下難得視野完整及保持自我的情懷之作。</strong><br />\n周生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為評論學會係會捧下危城、三人行，點估到係美人魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為佢地會捧擺渡人 (都有個推薦電影)，無人估到佢地會鍾意美人魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大會紀錄應該都唔少野睇，記得紅van果屆拗得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fb8fd47349203f69cbed89f0cec3c034d45476","tid":82773,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:47:28.000Z","msg":"林家棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樹大招風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371b1cf245c5fa1962fdd46e6762acd5ae4c5a35","tid":82773,"uid":6436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林家棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樹大招風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想林家棟同周冬雨拎金像獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}